# Assets Exposures Loans And Advances Provided Approved Limit Amount

## identifier
de8186

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, of the total committed amount, or limit, of loans and advances receivable, which were first provided during the relevant period.
     
Loans and advances are those financial assets categorised as "Loans and Receivables" in the accounting standards, other than "Trade Receivables" and "Cash".

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.ExposuresLoansAndAdvancesProvidedApprovedLimit.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.06
- period=duration
